<doc id="451660" wikidata="Q7273920" url="?curid=451660" title="R. Phillip Haire">
<text>Robert Phillip Haire (May 1, 1936 – October 8, 2024) was an American politician who was a Democratic member of the North Carolina House of Representatives representing District 119, covering Haywood, Jackson, Macon, and Swain counties. An attorney from Sylva, North Carolina, Haire served a total of seven terms in the state House. He announced in December 2011 that he would not seek another term in the House.

Haire died on October 8, 2024, at the age of 88.

