<doc id="451789" wikidata="Q6769711" url="?curid=451789" title="Mark Shulman (author)">
<text>Mark Shulman (born April 1, 1962, in Rochester, New York) is an American children&#x27;s author who has written more than 200 books. He is the founder of Oomf, Inc., a book production company.

Shulman lives with his family in New York City.

